snippet.title: Anomalous itinerant magnetism in single crystal Sr4Ru3O10: A thermodynamic and transport investigation
snippet.description: Anomalous itinerant magnetism in single crystal Sr4Ru3O10: A thermodynamic and transport investigation / Cao, G ; Chikara, S ; Brill, J W A thermodynamic and transport study of Sr4Ru3O10 as a function of temperature and magnetic field is presented. The central results include a growing specific heat C with increasing field B, a magnetic contribution to C/T at low temperatures proportional to -log(T), an abrupt jump and a peak in C/T at 2.90 T and 7 T for B||ab-plane and B||c-axis, respectively, and corresponding changes in the low T power laws of the resistivity.
